title: Tracy Morgan is back on form as he promises to get 30 Rock pregnant in first SNL promos - Fun
text: Tracy Morgan is definitely up to his old tricks â€“ if these new Saturday Night Live promos are any indication.The comedian is making his comedy comeback on Saturday, more than a year after he was seriously injured in a New Jersey car crash.Any concerns about Morgan's welfare are quickly allayed in the video above, when he vows to get the entirety of 30 Rock pregnant this week. That's the Tracy Morgan we know and love!Tracy is, of course, a former long-time cast member on SNL - known for characters like Safari Planet host Brian Fellow and Astronaut Jones.His special musical guest will be Demi Lovato, who is promoting her latest record Confident.Saturday Night Live airs at 11.30pm ET on NBC.
